'''repeater'''
# ([[firearm]]s) a [[gun]] that has a store of [[cartridge]]s and does not need [[reload]]ing after each shot.
# ([[ufology]] and similar studies) a person who regularly sees [[unexplained]] sightings of [[paranormal]] [[phenomenon]].
#: Note – this term is more commonly used by [[skeptic]]s of the paranormal, and [[implies]] that the witness lacks [[credibility]].